, female holotype 120 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Nepticulidae" genus="Hesperolyra" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hesperolyra saopaulensis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="saopaulensis">Hesperolyra saopaulensis</taxonomicName>
, female RMNH.INS.24505. Scale bars: 1 mm.
</paragraph>
